<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">ארם נהרים</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
ארם נהרים / 'ăram nahărayim / ar-am' nah-har-ah'-yim

===Etymology===
From [[ארם]] {{HH|758}} and the dual of [[נהר]] {{HH|5104}}; 

===Proper noun===
'''ארם נהרים'''

# Aram of (the) two rivers ([[Euphrates]] and [[Tigris]]) or Mesopotamia: - [[Aham-naharaim]], [[Mesopotamia]].

